# Verifier scratch artefacts. Verus historically emitted both compiled ELF
# binaries (files, ~4.3 MB each) AND scratch dirs into cwd; Phase 7's
# parallel run left ~1500 dirs and 334 binaries (totalling ~1.4 GB tracked)
# in the repo root. verus.py now runs each call inside a per-invocation
# tmpdir that is rmtree'd in `finally`; this rule covers both files and dirs
# so any other tool that drops `tmp*` scratch never reaches git.
tmp*
